Surgical Sciences nettoresultat steg
Surgical Science, vars aktie handlas på Nasdaq First North, redovisar ett nettoresultat för det tredje kvartalet 2019 på 10,2 miljoner kronor (-1,0).
07 Nov 2019, 07:47 by Nyhetsbyrån Direkt

Surgical Sciences net profit increased
Surgical Science, whose shares are traded on Nasdaq First North, reported a net profit for the third quarter of 2019 of SEK 10.2 million (-1.0).
07 Nov 2019, 07:47 by News Agency Direct
